WEBVTT

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:34.950
[Our Dazzling Days]

00:01:35.330 --> 00:01:37.780
[Episode 28]

00:01:41.310 --> 00:01:41.950
Xiaoman.

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:49.070
I-If it isn't Zhigang.

00:01:50.190 --> 00:01:51.390
What brings you here?

00:01:55.310 --> 00:01:56.400
It's been years.

00:01:57.310 --> 00:01:58.789
Can't I come and visit you?

00:01:59.950 --> 00:02:01.750
Now that you're back from Japan,

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:04.320
why not say hello
to the buddy you met there?

00:02:04.520 --> 00:02:05.380
Who do you mean?

00:02:05.510 --> 00:02:07.950
Was your brain broken
during the stay in Anning Hospital?

00:02:07.950 --> 00:02:08.710
I mean Yu.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:09.710
Yu?

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:10.560
I wouldn't have

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:13.360
known you were back from Japan
if Yu hadn't told me.

00:02:16.470 --> 00:02:18.870
So you're working for Yu Qiangbei now?

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:20.710
You really haven't changed a bit
over all these years,

00:02:20.710 --> 00:02:21.310
Xiaoman.

00:02:22.079 --> 00:02:24.240
Don't you see
how influential Yu is in Tiecheng now?

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:26.310
You're raising pigeons and farming here.

00:02:26.310 --> 00:02:29.079
That's nothing
compared to what Yu can give you, right?

00:02:29.079 --> 00:02:31.400
Give me what?
I'm just glad not to be tricked by him.

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:33.000
I'd rather stay out of his business.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:33.840
It's annoying as hell.

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:35.000
I don't know about the past
between you and him,

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:37.030
but don't you know
what Xia Lei has been doing lately?

00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:37.960
What do you mean?

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.980
I mean your close friend, Xia Lei,

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:43.130
is standing in Yu's way.

00:02:43.310 --> 00:02:44.520
That's why Yu sent me here to ask you

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:46.180
to try to talk Xia Lei out of it.

00:02:46.310 --> 00:02:47.400
But they're not connected.

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:49.329
Their businesses don't conflict.

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:51.870
That's not it. No cutting in line.
You got it?

00:02:51.870 --> 00:02:53.960
Yu and the factory already reached
an agreement to cooperate.

00:02:53.960 --> 00:02:55.020
It was all settled.

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:57.140
But now with Xia Lei's intrusion,

00:02:57.630 --> 00:02:59.470
Mr. Song has raised the price
without cause.

00:02:59.470 --> 00:03:01.270
This is not how business is done.

00:03:01.710 --> 00:03:02.710
It's true that Xia Lei

00:03:02.710 --> 00:03:05.710
has been faring quite well in Shanghai
over these years,

00:03:05.710 --> 00:03:07.240
doing a job in a big company.

00:03:07.910 --> 00:03:09.150
But that hardly means anything,

00:03:09.150 --> 00:03:10.000
since he doesn't call the shots.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.710
Talking to him won't change anything.

00:03:11.710 --> 00:03:12.840
Cut the crap.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.710
Just tell Xia Lei

00:03:13.710 --> 00:03:16.230
to leave the East Chemical Plant
within a week

00:03:16.230 --> 00:03:17.800
and stay out of all this stuff.

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:18.470
What now?

00:03:18.710 --> 00:03:19.680
Who does Yu think he is?

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:21.400
People have to go just because he says so?

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:22.030
Xiaoman,

00:03:22.910 --> 00:03:25.120
Yu specifically asked me to tell you this:

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:26.079
if Xia Lei fails

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:28.280
and Yu gives up on the acquisition,

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:30.280
the workers will have nowhere to go.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:33.310
Yu Qiangbei has a problem with me,

00:03:33.310 --> 00:03:35.079
so you're advising me
to leave the East Chemical Plant.

00:03:35.079 --> 00:03:36.010
What's with you?

00:03:36.430 --> 00:03:37.960
Do you even hear yourself, Xia Lei?

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:39.630
Would I ever do something like that?

00:03:39.630 --> 00:03:41.910
You have to take what I said seriously.

00:03:42.430 --> 00:03:43.960
Do consider it. You hear me?

00:03:44.120 --> 00:03:46.030
Yu is by no means a good person.

00:03:46.050 --> 00:03:48.310
He won't stop until he gets what he wants,

00:03:48.310 --> 00:03:50.430
and he's not shy
from trying extremely devious means.

00:03:50.430 --> 00:03:52.150
Really, you must take my advice to heart.

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:53.840
Do you think I'm afraid of him?

00:03:54.240 --> 00:03:56.079
That's not the issue here.

00:03:56.079 --> 00:03:59.040
The fact is,
you're blocking his path to wealth, right?

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:00.300
He's chasing you away.

00:04:00.590 --> 00:04:01.910
If you insist on staying,

00:04:01.910 --> 00:04:03.750
he'll mess with you. Don't you think?

00:04:03.750 --> 00:04:06.350
I can't watch you get hurt
and do nothing, can I?

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.030
I don't know about others

00:04:08.030 --> 00:04:10.000
or what exactly you guys are working on,

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.190
but I have faith in one thing.

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:13.910
That is, you will definitely

00:04:13.910 --> 00:04:16.120
defend the interests
of the factory workers.

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:17.310
After all, this is your home

00:04:17.310 --> 00:04:18.310
and where your parents live.

00:04:18.310 --> 00:04:19.970
All your friends are here too.

00:04:20.870 --> 00:04:22.120
Even though I want to,

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:24.000
I can't protect East Chemical Plant.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.200
I'm not even sure

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:26.510
if I'll be able

00:04:26.510 --> 00:04:27.830
to protect everyone.

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:31.950
I just found out

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:34.310
that me handing
the acquisition of Factory No. 3

00:04:34.310 --> 00:04:35.840
was a trap set up by someone.

00:04:36.270 --> 00:04:37.200
What do you mean?

00:04:37.830 --> 00:04:39.490
This is a double-edged sword.

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:40.750
It might hurt others

00:04:40.750 --> 00:04:42.010
and me at the same time.

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:44.159
I'm now thinking about how to

00:04:44.159 --> 00:04:46.020
extricate myself from this trap.

00:04:46.159 --> 00:04:47.600
Zhang Xiaoman, I'm back.

00:04:47.830 --> 00:04:48.750
I bought roast meat.

00:04:48.750 --> 00:04:49.480
You're back.

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:51.140
-Xia Lei is here.
-Xia Lei.

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:52.040
Chunchun.

00:04:52.040 --> 00:04:52.800
Let's eat.

00:04:53.070 --> 00:04:53.830
What did you buy? Show me.

00:04:53.830 --> 00:04:54.750
Da, Dongdong.

00:04:54.750 --> 00:04:56.310
Look who's here now!

00:04:57.510 --> 00:04:58.310
Let me help you with it.

00:04:58.310 --> 00:04:59.720
No need. No need.

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:00.150
Alright.

00:05:00.150 --> 00:05:00.870
Grass carp.

00:05:00.870 --> 00:05:02.040
What brought you here?

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:03.600
Nothing. I-I should get going now.

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:04.310
You guys eat.

00:05:04.310 --> 00:05:05.040
Where are you going?

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:05.800
What are you up to?

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:06.510
-Why leave?
-Eat with us.

00:05:06.510 --> 00:05:07.510
Which of them don't you know?

00:05:07.510 --> 00:05:09.070
W-Why don't you just eat with us?

00:05:09.070 --> 00:05:10.510
Don't leave. Eat with us here.

00:05:10.510 --> 00:05:11.510
I'm in a bad mood.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:13.430
A drink with us will cheer you up.

00:05:13.430 --> 00:05:14.560
Sit, Dongdong. Take a seat.

00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:16.220
Why leave? You must stay here.

00:05:16.310 --> 00:05:17.120
A clink of glasses?

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:18.600
-Come on.
-Xia Lei, bottoms up.

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:19.920
Guys, cheers. Down it.

00:05:22.360 --> 00:05:23.190
Go easy on it.

00:05:27.020 --> 00:05:27.950
Is this ready to be eaten?

00:05:27.950 --> 00:05:29.600
"Ready"? It's almost burnt.

00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:30.630
Look at the flames.

00:05:30.630 --> 00:05:32.030
Who are all these people?

00:05:32.270 --> 00:05:33.190
Shi!

00:05:33.510 --> 00:05:35.510
Why did no one invite me for this party?

00:05:35.510 --> 00:05:37.159
Did you find money in the streets or what?

00:05:37.159 --> 00:05:38.800
You've actually brought gifts to my place.

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.270
This rarely happens.

00:05:40.510 --> 00:05:41.970
Did I say these are for you?

00:05:42.070 --> 00:05:43.360
They're for Xia Lei.

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:44.240
Look at you,

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:45.310
such a goof.

00:05:45.310 --> 00:05:46.240
Why me?

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:47.040
A beer for you.

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:48.520
Gosh. Yeah, let's drink.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:49.630
I bet Shi is up for no good.

00:05:49.630 --> 00:05:51.230
His eyes have given him away.

00:05:51.780 --> 00:05:53.270
What? I just fancy a gathering
with you guys.

00:05:53.270 --> 00:05:54.400
You never invite me.

00:05:55.159 --> 00:05:55.800
Xia Lei,

00:05:56.310 --> 00:05:58.970
I heard
you're looking to acquire Factory No. 3.

00:06:00.510 --> 00:06:02.680
I'm not. The company I work for is.

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:03.720
Great.

00:06:04.220 --> 00:06:06.160
A man of our own is handling the buyout.

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.960
No fear of losing my job
anymore.

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:09.600
Why not

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:11.000
l-let me propose a toast?

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:13.430
Well... I won't say much.

00:06:13.480 --> 00:06:15.080
For your huge contribution,

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:16.180
I'll take a big sip.

00:06:17.510 --> 00:06:19.830
Come on, it's time to enjoy the food.

00:06:19.830 --> 00:06:20.720
Shi, listen,

00:06:21.040 --> 00:06:23.040
d-don't bring up that buyout stuff.

00:06:23.270 --> 00:06:23.720
Da.

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:25.120
-Cheers.
-Come on, Lei.

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:25.560
I...

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:28.120
I was talking about the acquisition

00:06:28.210 --> 00:06:29.310
o-of Factory No. 3.

00:06:29.310 --> 00:06:31.710
Why did you have to make me
drop the subject?

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:32.700
So you did realize it.

00:06:32.700 --> 00:06:34.159
I was afraid you wouldn't.

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:35.510
J-Just don't talk about

00:06:35.510 --> 00:06:36.950
that stuff in the middle of dinner.

00:06:36.950 --> 00:06:38.510
You can do fine making popcorn at home.

00:06:38.510 --> 00:06:39.630
Why worry about the factory at all?

00:06:39.630 --> 00:06:41.490
Should that even be your concern?

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:44.159
Xia Lei,

00:06:44.159 --> 00:06:45.510
I-I have something to say.

00:06:45.510 --> 00:06:47.170
Hope it won't sound too harsh.

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:49.720
I heard from Zhigang...

00:06:50.630 --> 00:06:52.950
that Yu intends to buy the factory.

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:56.400
He's offering more to the workers
than you are.

00:06:57.170 --> 00:06:58.870
I don't care what others' plans are.

00:06:58.870 --> 00:07:00.270
But you're one of the factory folks.

00:07:00.270 --> 00:07:01.800
You can't leave everyone homeless

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:03.860
just for that little salary of yours.

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.190
What's that about now? H-Has Lei done

00:07:05.190 --> 00:07:06.400
anything to leave anyone homeless?

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:07.590
What has he done?

00:07:07.610 --> 00:07:08.940
So you believe Zhigang?

00:07:09.390 --> 00:07:10.160
If that's the case,

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:11.000
take his side then.

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:11.950
Don't hang with us.

00:07:11.950 --> 00:07:13.360
Why should I take his side?

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:15.480
T-That's not going to happen.

00:07:15.800 --> 00:07:18.060
I admit that Zhigang is not a good person.

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.720
But think about this:
for us who want to stay,

00:07:22.310 --> 00:07:24.950
all we want is shelter and food, right?

00:07:25.600 --> 00:07:28.000
We don't care
who pays the factory how much.

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:31.120
We're all for the person who can guarantee
we'll have 3 meals a day.

00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:32.510
If our livelihoods are destroyed,

00:07:32.510 --> 00:07:34.159
w-will any of us be happy?

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:36.510
Lei is not destroying anyone's livelihood.

00:07:36.510 --> 00:07:37.800
What's the point of saying this to him?

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:39.070
Has he taken food off your table or what?

00:07:39.070 --> 00:07:40.000
You can make as much porpcorn

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:40.510
as you want at home.

00:07:40.510 --> 00:07:41.480
Has anyone stopped you?

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:42.920
I'm talking about Factory No. 3,

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:44.210
yet you keep deflecting it
to making popcorn.

00:07:44.210 --> 00:07:46.390
W-Why do you have to do that?

00:07:46.510 --> 00:07:47.720
You complain about not having work
every day.

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:48.720
I've asked you to be a moving worker,

00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:50.480
but you just want to be a lazy glutton.

00:07:50.480 --> 00:07:51.750
Why do you have to spew nonsense

00:07:51.750 --> 00:07:52.680
like a nag now?

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:56.540
Alright, come on.

00:07:56.540 --> 00:07:58.180
Have some meat. Take this.

00:07:58.480 --> 00:07:59.560
Alright. Let's drink.

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:00.390
N-No way.

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:01.720
This is what I think.

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:04.000
I consider those who drink
at the same table as me

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:05.660
to be my friends and brothers.

00:08:06.530 --> 00:08:08.260
But now, Xia Lei is not doing...

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:09.540
t-the right thing.

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.800
It seems he doesn't take us seriously

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:13.870
or care if we'll live or die,

00:08:13.870 --> 00:08:14.800
though we're...

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:15.600
Alright.

00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:16.830
Shi, listen to me.

00:08:17.630 --> 00:08:19.430
Yu Qiangbei's offer will eventually

00:08:19.430 --> 00:08:20.630
lead to your doom.

00:08:21.070 --> 00:08:22.510
I am indeed following work procedures,

00:08:22.510 --> 00:08:23.680
but I have my own reason for doing so.

00:08:23.680 --> 00:08:25.630
I wish I could convince
the company I work for

00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:27.750
to act
in the factory workers' best interest.

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:29.750
I crave to make the whole thing work.

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:33.280
G-Guys, listen.

00:08:33.630 --> 00:08:35.000
The first thing you should do now

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.669
is go out and have a look.

00:08:36.980 --> 00:08:38.000
Tremendous changes

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.000
are taking place in the outside world.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.909
Do you have to stick with
the East Chemical Plant

00:08:40.909 --> 00:08:42.640
and wait for others to feed you?

00:08:51.710 --> 00:08:53.040
Who asked you to feed us?

00:08:53.120 --> 00:08:54.750
D-Does any of us need feeding by you?

00:08:54.750 --> 00:08:56.630
I-I came here to talk to you
about the acquisition,

00:08:56.630 --> 00:08:58.910
yet you think I-I'm begging you
for a handout?

00:08:58.910 --> 00:09:00.600
Don't eat with us then, alright?

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:01.860
Go eat somewhere else.

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:03.120
I won't ask you for charity

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:04.200
even if I'm out of options.

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.600
Make no mistake, Xia Lei!

00:09:05.910 --> 00:09:07.390
I thought we were good friends
in childhood.

00:09:07.390 --> 00:09:08.920
But when I talk to you now...

00:09:08.970 --> 00:09:09.520
Oh, crap!

00:09:09.630 --> 00:09:11.210
You don't deserve my liquor.

00:09:11.210 --> 00:09:12.750
You think I want it? Take it away!

00:09:12.750 --> 00:09:14.720
I-I came here to talk to you in good will,

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:16.780
yet you said all that gibberish to me.

00:09:17.900 --> 00:09:18.780
Ignore him.

00:09:19.180 --> 00:09:20.030
-Is the meat ready?
-It's typical

00:09:20.030 --> 00:09:21.510
of Shi to behave like that
after a few drinks.

00:09:21.510 --> 00:09:22.510
Come on, let's drink.

00:09:22.510 --> 00:09:23.750
However, Xia Lei...

00:09:24.510 --> 00:09:26.870
What Shi just said was harsh and snarky.

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:28.500
But frankly speaking,

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:30.840
not everyone gets to go to Shanghai,

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:33.650
and not everyone wants to be there.

00:09:33.870 --> 00:09:35.960
Shanghai wouldn't be the way it is now
without these workers.

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:37.200
Could the skyscrapers

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:38.840
there have built themselves?

00:09:38.840 --> 00:09:39.910
I've heard about

00:09:39.910 --> 00:09:42.320
that wolf-like corporate culture of yours.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:44.440
There was a discussion about it
back in Japan.

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:47.240
But... But we're not wolves.

00:09:47.270 --> 00:09:48.670
We're humans, aren't we?

00:09:48.790 --> 00:09:51.520
Honestly,
sometimes I envy you for being content

00:09:53.910 --> 00:09:55.640
with muddling through each day

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:58.290
and not thinking about the future.

00:09:58.480 --> 00:09:59.810
What do you mean by that?

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:02.480
Who's not thinking about the future?

00:10:02.480 --> 00:10:05.320
We're building a future
simply by living our lives well here.

00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:06.910
How can you say
we don't care about the future?

00:10:06.910 --> 00:10:08.200
Do you mean only you guys
who left town have a future

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:10.320
and we who chose to stay don't have one?

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:11.390
What now? Is our future

00:10:11.390 --> 00:10:12.720
worthless in your eyes?

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:23.210
Where are you going?

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:24.560
-Xia Lei.
-Xia Lei!

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:25.760
Don't ask him to stay!

00:10:28.910 --> 00:10:29.970
Let's have a drink.

00:10:30.120 --> 00:10:30.910
Sure. Let's drink.

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:32.510
Drink up, come on.

00:10:34.750 --> 00:10:36.600
-Let's drink.
-Come on.

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:50.560
What are you doing
so early in the morning?

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:52.890
You're up? I'm planting flowers out here.

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:54.780
Keep me company, will you?

00:10:58.530 --> 00:11:00.530
Last night, it just occurred to me

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:03.720
that we could plant some lilies
in the yard.

00:11:06.030 --> 00:11:07.320
That won't work.

00:11:07.720 --> 00:11:09.360
It's too cold here.

00:11:11.060 --> 00:11:12.670
You're underestimating these lilies.

00:11:12.670 --> 00:11:14.510
They're actually cold-resistant.

00:11:14.510 --> 00:11:16.100
If the weather gets freezing,

00:11:16.100 --> 00:11:17.970
just lay a plastic sheet over them.

00:11:17.970 --> 00:11:19.290
As long as the roots are fine,

00:11:19.290 --> 00:11:21.490
they will bloom just the same next year.

00:11:21.720 --> 00:11:22.510
Right.

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:25.920
As long as the roots are fine.

00:11:26.360 --> 00:11:27.560
Roots are important.

00:11:28.170 --> 00:11:29.970
I thought the same back in Japan.

00:11:30.840 --> 00:11:31.720
Though I was there,

00:11:31.720 --> 00:11:35.720
I knew my roots
belonged in the East Chemical Plant,

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:37.080
and that I could always

00:11:37.080 --> 00:11:39.150
come back if anything happened.

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:40.820
But what about the future?

00:11:41.910 --> 00:11:43.910
Where will my roots be in the future?

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:46.390
Do you remember

00:11:46.390 --> 00:11:47.840
you once took me

00:11:47.840 --> 00:11:49.240
to the factory cemetery?

00:11:49.910 --> 00:11:51.240
At that time, I asked you

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:54.510
if it would be a regret
for those whose roots

00:11:54.510 --> 00:11:56.720
weren't here to be buried here.

00:11:57.270 --> 00:11:58.670
Later, I figured it out.

00:11:59.510 --> 00:12:00.750
For those people,

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:03.080
wherever they were originally from

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:04.540
or wherever they had to go,

00:12:05.270 --> 00:12:07.000
as long as they grew up here,

00:12:07.670 --> 00:12:09.930
remembered their families all the time,

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:11.880
and kept all that in mind,

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:13.910
their roots would be here forever.

00:12:13.910 --> 00:12:15.270
You have your thoughts.

00:12:15.510 --> 00:12:17.270
You have your things to do.

00:12:17.320 --> 00:12:19.240
Just act on what your heart tells you.

00:12:19.240 --> 00:12:21.100
I'll always be supportive of you.

00:12:22.510 --> 00:12:23.390
Okay.

00:12:26.030 --> 00:12:27.830
However this place ends up like,

00:12:27.870 --> 00:12:29.600
our roots will be here the same.

00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:31.240
I'm not going anywhere.

00:12:33.030 --> 00:12:34.560
How can they do this? Right?

00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:36.120
Making us move just like that?

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:37.790
Most of you are senior to me.
I'm in no position

00:12:37.790 --> 00:12:39.670
to say anything,
but this just feels wrong.

00:12:39.670 --> 00:12:41.070
What's written up there?

00:12:41.840 --> 00:12:44.240
Mr. Zhuang,
it says the relocation is confirmed.

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:45.720
-You had no idea at all?
-Relocation?

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:46.630
Where to?

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:48.630
To Yingkou, the whole community.

00:12:48.630 --> 00:12:50.440
How can they do this?

00:12:50.600 --> 00:12:51.720
We've lived here for most of our lives.

00:12:51.720 --> 00:12:52.850
How can we just move?

00:12:53.120 --> 00:12:53.870
Yeah. This is...

00:12:53.870 --> 00:12:54.480
Zhuang.

00:12:55.150 --> 00:12:55.790
Zhuang!

00:12:56.510 --> 00:12:57.510
What happened?

00:12:57.750 --> 00:12:59.120
This is not about money.

00:12:59.140 --> 00:13:00.540
The decision to relocate

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:01.800
the factory is final.

00:13:02.550 --> 00:13:04.790
Moving an entire factory this big?

00:13:04.810 --> 00:13:06.410
Don't tell Yan about it.

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:07.320
The notice is right here.

00:13:07.320 --> 00:13:09.000
He'll see it when he walks by.

00:13:09.240 --> 00:13:10.500
I'll tear it down then.

00:13:10.840 --> 00:13:11.750
Just go home.

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:13.390
You'll tear it down, right?

00:13:13.390 --> 00:13:14.550
Yes. Go home now.

00:13:20.620 --> 00:13:21.750
That's right. Tear it down!

00:13:21.750 --> 00:13:22.600
Great. Good job!

00:13:22.600 --> 00:13:24.240
-Let's see what they can do about it.
-Well done!

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:25.960
Yeah. I'll rip every piece off.

00:13:25.960 --> 00:13:27.020
We're not leaving!

00:13:27.320 --> 00:13:28.650
What are you looking at?

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:31.030
Why are they making so much noise?

00:13:31.030 --> 00:13:32.320
For some posted ads.

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:34.370
All is fine.
You have nothing to do with it.

00:13:34.370 --> 00:13:35.320
Go take a seat.

00:13:35.320 --> 00:13:36.320
Got it. None of my business.

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:37.870
I'll go make lunch for you.

00:13:37.870 --> 00:13:38.870
-Okay.
-Alright?

00:13:51.230 --> 00:13:53.280
Mom, what's going on outside?

00:13:54.790 --> 00:13:57.190
The East Chemical Plant
is to be relocated.

00:13:57.630 --> 00:13:58.490
Out of a sudden?

00:13:59.510 --> 00:14:00.320
It was also a shock to me.

00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:02.840
There was a word about it on the streets,

00:14:03.080 --> 00:14:04.760
yet I didn't expect such a big factory

00:14:04.760 --> 00:14:06.420
would be moved just like that.

00:14:08.200 --> 00:14:09.330
Look at your father.

00:14:09.440 --> 00:14:12.370
He's been getting better every day
since we got here.

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:15.050
His memory has improved a lot, too.

00:14:15.120 --> 00:14:16.360
What if he finds out the truth?

00:14:16.360 --> 00:14:17.840
Don't tell him about the relocation.

00:14:17.840 --> 00:14:19.300
Let's all keep it from him.

00:14:25.840 --> 00:14:26.770
What's going on?

00:14:28.750 --> 00:14:29.360
Freeze!

00:14:30.840 --> 00:14:31.510
Mom, are you okay?

00:14:31.510 --> 00:14:32.600
Yes. But...

00:14:33.960 --> 00:14:35.360
Alright. Just sit down.

00:14:35.360 --> 00:14:36.620
I-I'll go check it out.

00:14:38.440 --> 00:14:39.440
Do be careful,

00:14:39.440 --> 00:14:40.270
Xia Lei.

00:14:44.510 --> 00:14:45.240
You good?

00:14:45.630 --> 00:14:46.320
Yes, all good.

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:46.910
Did you get hurt?

00:14:46.910 --> 00:14:47.840
No. Go check on Mom.

00:14:47.840 --> 00:14:48.670
Watch out for the broken glass.

00:14:48.670 --> 00:14:49.440
Just go check on Mom.

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:50.370
Did you get hurt?

00:14:50.390 --> 00:14:53.030
No. Why would this happen?

00:14:53.030 --> 00:14:55.360
Acquiring the factory
is supposed to be a happy thing.

00:14:55.360 --> 00:14:57.510
How... did it turn out like this?

00:14:57.910 --> 00:14:58.720
Dad, Mom.

00:14:58.910 --> 00:14:59.770
How about this?

00:15:00.360 --> 00:15:01.840
Let me take you to a hotel.

00:15:01.870 --> 00:15:02.480
No!

00:15:03.720 --> 00:15:05.240
Let's see what else they'll do.

00:15:05.240 --> 00:15:07.440
If they dare smash our home again,
I'll show them.

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:08.770
We won't hide anywhere.

00:15:12.550 --> 00:15:13.290
Zhang Xiaoman.

00:15:13.290 --> 00:15:14.020
You're back.

00:15:16.360 --> 00:15:17.890
Xia Lei's home was smashed.

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:21.870
Who did it?

00:15:21.870 --> 00:15:22.960
I heard it was because of

00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:24.870
Xia Lei's attempt to acquire the factory.

00:15:24.870 --> 00:15:26.120
Yu spread rumors

00:15:26.120 --> 00:15:28.120
that the workers wouldn't get paid
if it came true.

00:15:28.120 --> 00:15:29.510
It would surely anger the workers.

00:15:29.510 --> 00:15:30.650
Money means everything to them.

00:15:30.650 --> 00:15:31.600
So they smashed Lei's home.

00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:34.000
What an outrage.
How could they have done that?

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:34.650
I'll go take a look.

00:15:34.650 --> 00:15:35.650
Why?

00:15:36.510 --> 00:15:38.200
Aren't you mad at Lei now?

00:15:38.280 --> 00:15:39.810
You should take this chance

00:15:39.870 --> 00:15:42.120
to let him know what it feels like
to be deserted by everyone,

00:15:42.120 --> 00:15:43.320
even his best friend.

00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:46.320
I see Lei as my own brother.

00:15:46.840 --> 00:15:49.190
We can fight all we want
behind closed doors,

00:15:49.190 --> 00:15:50.950
but I won't let anyone hurt him.

00:15:53.360 --> 00:15:55.630
I knew no one could be more loyal
than you.

00:15:56.910 --> 00:15:58.120
Alright, you stay at home.

00:15:58.120 --> 00:15:58.810
I'll go check on him.

00:15:58.810 --> 00:16:00.010
Mind your own safety.

00:16:01.640 --> 00:16:02.950
This is not how things

00:16:03.200 --> 00:16:04.120
should be done,

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:04.630
right?

00:16:04.670 --> 00:16:05.600
-Right.
-Right!

00:16:05.630 --> 00:16:07.440
Look, let's stay in the loop

00:16:07.440 --> 00:16:08.840
and keep each other updated, okay?

00:16:08.840 --> 00:16:09.910
-Okay.
-Sure.

00:16:09.910 --> 00:16:11.510
If you get any news, share it.

00:16:11.510 --> 00:16:12.510
-Sure.
-Let's go.

00:16:14.750 --> 00:16:16.010
Such a pain in the neck.

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:17.880
What were you guys doing?

00:16:19.200 --> 00:16:21.030
Just talking about the relocation.

00:16:21.030 --> 00:16:23.150
There are different versions of the story
now.

00:16:23.150 --> 00:16:25.000
So I thought I'd ask around to see

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:26.200
what truly happened.

00:16:26.890 --> 00:16:29.130
Listen, make inquiries all your want.

00:16:29.480 --> 00:16:30.740
Just leave Xia Lei out.

00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.580
So what if I talk about him?

00:16:32.670 --> 00:16:34.070
What do you mean by that?

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:36.550
That day, you got drunk

00:16:36.550 --> 00:16:37.510
and quarreled with him.

00:16:37.510 --> 00:16:39.110
Now you want to badmouth him?

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:40.720
I just have to let everyone know

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:42.320
what kind of person Xia Lei has become.

00:16:42.320 --> 00:16:43.720
Hey, what's that coming from?

00:16:43.720 --> 00:16:45.030
Lei has a job in Shanghai now.

00:16:45.030 --> 00:16:46.910
The buyout is a corporate decision.
What does he have to do with it?

00:16:46.910 --> 00:16:48.910
I'm telling you,
he's choosing his small paycheck

00:16:48.910 --> 00:16:50.510
over the future of everyone.

00:16:50.550 --> 00:16:52.320
Upon knowing how Xia Lei is handling this,

00:16:52.320 --> 00:16:54.050
those people all went furious.

00:16:54.790 --> 00:16:56.920
It's impossible to get through to you.

00:16:57.390 --> 00:16:59.080
Fine. I don't care about anything else,

00:16:59.080 --> 00:17:00.440
and you can chat all you want,

00:17:00.440 --> 00:17:02.120
but just leave Xia Lei out of it,

00:17:02.120 --> 00:17:02.650
alright?

00:17:02.670 --> 00:17:03.730
Do you understand?

00:17:03.830 --> 00:17:04.550
No, I don't.

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:05.720
What don't you understand?

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:06.109
Wait.

00:17:06.109 --> 00:17:07.400
Are you on his side now?

00:17:08.190 --> 00:17:08.920
So what then?

00:17:08.920 --> 00:17:10.270
H-How can you side with him?

00:17:10.270 --> 00:17:11.310
And you have the gall to say "so what"?

00:17:11.310 --> 00:17:12.349
I'm only asking you
not to speak ill of him.

00:17:12.349 --> 00:17:12.829
What's the matter with...

00:17:12.829 --> 00:17:13.510
Who are you

00:17:13.510 --> 00:17:14.510
to give me a warning?

00:17:14.510 --> 00:17:16.920
Just leave him out.
What don't you understand?

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:18.589
Even you are backing him now.

00:17:18.589 --> 00:17:20.310
You're no good either, Xiaoman.

00:17:20.310 --> 00:17:21.550
What's wrong with you two?

00:17:21.550 --> 00:17:23.069
You're asking for a beating, seriously.

00:17:23.069 --> 00:17:23.829
Beat me then!

00:17:23.829 --> 00:17:25.359
You never do anything good!

00:17:27.510 --> 00:17:29.920
There are many days before the move.

00:17:30.790 --> 00:17:33.310
Isn't it a bit early to start packing now?

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:37.010
Go over the things
and decide what to discard.

00:17:37.340 --> 00:17:39.940
That'll save us a hassle
when it's time to move.

00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:41.550
Once we leave...

00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:45.240
there will be no coming back.

00:17:59.200 --> 00:17:59.830
Mom,

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:02.440
are you sure of moving to Yingkou

00:18:02.720 --> 00:18:04.050
with the factory folks?

00:18:05.310 --> 00:18:06.640
I'm a bit concerned.

00:18:07.070 --> 00:18:09.470
How about you come live with me
in Shanghai?

00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:11.840
If we move to your place,

00:18:12.880 --> 00:18:15.480
what will people say about us
behind our backs?

00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:20.310
Mom, you can't live your life
by others' opinions, right?

00:18:20.310 --> 00:18:22.710
They get to wag their tongues
all they want.

00:18:23.000 --> 00:18:23.750
Besides,

00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:24.920
whether I'm here or not,

00:18:24.920 --> 00:18:26.510
Factory No. 3 will be sold just the same.

00:18:26.510 --> 00:18:29.040
The East Chemical Plant
will soon cease to be.

00:18:31.110 --> 00:18:31.960
Xia Lei.

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:36.270
You're wrong.

00:18:38.880 --> 00:18:40.030
The East Chemical Plant is a cash cow.

00:18:40.030 --> 00:18:42.000
Those people can fight over the scraps
all they want.

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:43.110
I don't have a say in it.

00:18:43.110 --> 00:18:44.640
But you can't be one of them.

00:18:44.750 --> 00:18:45.750
This is your home,

00:18:45.750 --> 00:18:47.070
where you were raised.

00:18:49.880 --> 00:18:51.070
Your mom and I don't know

00:18:51.070 --> 00:18:52.400
much about your job.

00:18:53.820 --> 00:18:55.130
But how could you not tell us

00:18:55.130 --> 00:18:57.460
anything about a massive issue like this?

00:19:03.110 --> 00:19:04.840
It turns out we have spent years

00:19:05.310 --> 00:19:06.440
raising an ingrate!

00:19:08.070 --> 00:19:09.070
What a disgrace.

00:19:12.130 --> 00:19:12.730
Take this.

00:19:25.110 --> 00:19:25.870
Eat up.

00:19:26.160 --> 00:19:26.790
Who is it?

00:19:29.310 --> 00:19:29.910
Dongdong.

00:19:30.640 --> 00:19:31.510
What brings you here?

00:19:31.510 --> 00:19:33.040
I-I'm here to see your wife.

00:19:33.510 --> 00:19:34.110
For what?

00:19:34.240 --> 00:19:35.110
I just need to ask

00:19:35.110 --> 00:19:36.790
your wife a q-question.

00:19:37.890 --> 00:19:38.820
A question, huh?

00:19:39.270 --> 00:19:40.880
Fine.
I'd love to know what you have to ask.

00:19:40.880 --> 00:19:42.570
Come here, my love. Sit in this chair.

00:19:42.570 --> 00:19:44.270
Come on. Let's hear what he has to say.

00:19:44.270 --> 00:19:45.350
What is it now, Shi?

00:19:45.350 --> 00:19:46.590
Go ahead. Ask her.

00:19:47.810 --> 00:19:49.010
O-Okay. Here it goes.

00:19:50.110 --> 00:19:51.480
Do you know who

00:19:51.480 --> 00:19:53.030
the factory will be sold to?

00:19:53.510 --> 00:19:54.880
How am I supposed to answer that?

00:19:54.880 --> 00:19:55.350
You see...

00:19:55.350 --> 00:19:56.310
I have no idea at all.

00:19:56.310 --> 00:19:58.110
After barging into
the Plant Director's office

00:19:58.110 --> 00:19:59.480
and quarreling with Xia Lei,

00:19:59.480 --> 00:20:00.350
you still couldn't get an answer.

00:20:00.350 --> 00:20:01.000
My wife is a mere HR staffer.

00:20:01.000 --> 00:20:02.530
What can she possibly know?

00:20:03.510 --> 00:20:04.640
Dongdong, what got into you?

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:06.070
Did you wake up
on the wrong side of the bed

00:20:06.070 --> 00:20:07.930
or what? Why are you upset with me?

00:20:07.940 --> 00:20:08.900
Upset with you?

00:20:09.510 --> 00:20:10.440
Let me ask you.

00:20:10.440 --> 00:20:11.350
Someone smashed a window

00:20:11.350 --> 00:20:13.240
of Xia Lei's home. Did you know that?

00:20:13.240 --> 00:20:14.510
Y-Yes, I heard about it.

00:20:14.510 --> 00:20:16.310
You heard about it?
It must be you who smashed it!

00:20:16.310 --> 00:20:17.720
"Heard about it"? Crap!

00:20:18.400 --> 00:20:18.880
Gosh.

00:20:19.110 --> 00:20:20.400
What kind of person do you think I am,
Dongdong?

00:20:20.400 --> 00:20:23.070
C-Could I have smashed
a window of Xia Lei's home?

00:20:23.070 --> 00:20:24.720
You're exactly that kind of person.

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:26.920
Even if you hadn't, it must've been done
by someone who heard

00:20:26.920 --> 00:20:28.350
the nonsense you've been talking outside.

00:20:28.350 --> 00:20:28.920
That's what you're like.

00:20:28.920 --> 00:20:31.520
Y-You're accusing me
of something I didn't do.

00:20:32.310 --> 00:20:33.640
Dongdong, let's get this straight.

00:20:33.640 --> 00:20:35.510
X-Xiaoman and I

00:20:35.510 --> 00:20:36.720
have the same mentor.

00:20:37.720 --> 00:20:39.270
H-He's also Xia Lei's best friend.

00:20:39.270 --> 00:20:40.310
That goes without saying.

00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:42.310
G-Given all these connections,

00:20:42.310 --> 00:20:44.720
would I ever be mad at Xia Lei for real?

00:20:45.000 --> 00:20:47.720
That day, it was just the alcohol talking.

00:20:47.720 --> 00:20:49.720
Can that angry talk be taken seriously?

00:20:49.720 --> 00:20:51.110
Listen, rumors are spreading

00:20:51.110 --> 00:20:53.310
like wildfire in the factory now.

00:20:53.310 --> 00:20:54.510
You're not there, so you don't know.

00:20:54.510 --> 00:20:56.310
But Lulu is.
She definitely knows the truth.

00:20:56.310 --> 00:20:57.030
Please, Shi.

00:20:57.030 --> 00:20:58.510
Why do you keep dragging me into this?

00:20:58.510 --> 00:21:01.350
How would I know the truth?
The area's buzzing with rumors.

00:21:01.350 --> 00:21:03.110
T-The fact that I came talk to you

00:21:03.110 --> 00:21:04.880
means I consider you as my family.

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:07.680
Dongdong,
I regard you as a little brother of mine.

00:21:07.840 --> 00:21:10.990
Back when the factory
first started struggling,

00:21:11.350 --> 00:21:12.680
I-I made a big fuss about it

00:21:12.680 --> 00:21:15.310
and declared to make popcorn
with my father-in-law.

00:21:15.310 --> 00:21:16.920
But I didn't mean any of that.

00:21:16.920 --> 00:21:18.400
I said it only to comfort myself.

00:21:18.400 --> 00:21:20.800
What did my wife see in me
in the first place?

00:21:21.460 --> 00:21:23.910
It was my job as a factory worker,
wasn't it?

00:21:24.710 --> 00:21:27.060
You've all left the factory
during these years.

00:21:27.060 --> 00:21:28.520
Why would I choose to stay?

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:31.160
I don't have big ambitions.

00:21:31.590 --> 00:21:33.720
I just want to stick around as a worker.

00:21:35.720 --> 00:21:37.790
You can't possibly know how I feel now.

00:21:37.790 --> 00:21:40.160
The factory is dying, and I'm terrified.

00:21:40.710 --> 00:21:41.710
Serves you right.

00:21:43.750 --> 00:21:44.880
It serves him right.

00:21:45.250 --> 00:21:48.050
Who knows what the future holds?

00:21:48.150 --> 00:21:49.750
You're panicking too early.

00:21:50.110 --> 00:21:51.790
There's one thing I can guarantee.

00:21:51.790 --> 00:21:53.520
Xia Lei is not the kind of person

00:21:54.370 --> 00:21:57.030
who throws his friends and family
under the bus.

00:21:57.310 --> 00:21:58.400
That's for sure.

00:21:58.830 --> 00:21:59.830
Isn't it obvious?

00:22:00.120 --> 00:22:01.960
Dongdong, mark what I'm going to say.

00:22:01.960 --> 00:22:03.640
Pass it along to Xia Lei

00:22:03.640 --> 00:22:04.880
if you get a chance.

00:22:05.260 --> 00:22:07.260
If the factory is bought by Xia Lei,

00:22:07.920 --> 00:22:08.920
I, Shi Dongming, will be

00:22:08.920 --> 00:22:10.720
the first one to follow his lead.

00:22:10.790 --> 00:22:11.720
Who is Lei?

00:22:11.720 --> 00:22:13.310
Lei is one of our family.

00:22:13.590 --> 00:22:14.920
If I d-don't trust him,

00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:16.110
who else can I trust?

00:22:16.450 --> 00:22:17.210
Am I right?

00:22:18.870 --> 00:22:19.390
Right.

00:22:19.460 --> 00:22:20.660
What do you say, Lulu?

00:22:22.030 --> 00:22:22.550
Right.

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:24.110
That settles it, doesn't it?

00:22:24.110 --> 00:22:25.710
Isn't that all there is to it?

00:22:26.190 --> 00:22:27.720
I'll leave you to your dinner.

00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:29.250
Y-You... I-I'll get going.

00:22:30.030 --> 00:22:31.830
Let me know if you learn any news.

00:22:38.220 --> 00:22:40.220
S-So he thinks he's in the right now?

00:22:41.480 --> 00:22:44.000
Sweetie, what's all this about?

00:22:44.310 --> 00:22:46.440
Everyone is saying he has betrayed us.

00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:49.400
We watched Xia Lei grow up.

00:22:49.640 --> 00:22:52.900
He doesn't seem like the kind of kid
who would do bad things.

00:22:53.750 --> 00:22:55.850
He's looking to acquire Factory No. 3.

00:22:55.850 --> 00:22:57.580
A misunderstanding happened.

00:22:57.920 --> 00:22:59.160
Factory No. 3?

00:22:59.510 --> 00:23:00.720
Factory No. 3...

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:03.110
has been out of operation for a long time.

00:23:03.110 --> 00:23:04.640
Do the machines still work?

00:23:13.340 --> 00:23:14.010
Zhuang!

00:23:14.640 --> 00:23:16.110
I've been looking everywhere for you.

00:23:16.110 --> 00:23:16.960
Yan?

00:23:17.270 --> 00:23:18.000
Hurry and come with me.

00:23:18.000 --> 00:23:18.960
Something happened. Come on.

00:23:18.960 --> 00:23:20.640
Wait till I finish this chess game.

00:23:20.640 --> 00:23:22.070
What's the point of this now?

00:23:22.070 --> 00:23:23.240
Yan, what's with you?

00:23:23.240 --> 00:23:24.100
This is urgent!

00:23:24.110 --> 00:23:25.310
-What's urgent?
-What's urgent?

00:23:25.310 --> 00:23:26.840
A matter about the factory.

00:23:26.960 --> 00:23:27.370
Let's go!

00:23:27.370 --> 00:23:27.880
Go!

00:23:28.310 --> 00:23:29.240
Let's go!

00:23:29.240 --> 00:23:30.160
Hurry!

00:23:31.590 --> 00:23:32.590
Yan, slow down.

00:23:32.590 --> 00:23:33.920
We're not riding bikes.

00:23:34.240 --> 00:23:35.440
Keep up. Keep up!

00:23:36.410 --> 00:23:37.170
Get a move on!

00:23:38.060 --> 00:23:39.500
Yan, not so fast.

00:23:43.790 --> 00:23:44.400
Mr. Song.

00:23:45.020 --> 00:23:46.030
The purpose of my visit

00:23:46.030 --> 00:23:47.510
is to know more

00:23:47.890 --> 00:23:48.960
about Yu Qiangbei.

00:23:49.510 --> 00:23:50.960
Are you familiar with him?

00:23:50.960 --> 00:23:51.690
I know of him.

00:23:52.510 --> 00:23:54.920
Now that he's asking to buy the factory,

00:23:54.920 --> 00:23:56.160
why not sell it to him?

00:23:58.680 --> 00:23:59.750
I'm not exactly

00:23:59.750 --> 00:24:00.880
familiar with him.

00:24:01.110 --> 00:24:04.640
He was among the first private business
owners who looked to contract the factory.

00:24:04.640 --> 00:24:05.720
But I know this person never

00:24:05.720 --> 00:24:07.780
plays by the rules in doing business.

00:24:08.140 --> 00:24:09.400
He proposed to develop

00:24:09.510 --> 00:24:12.110
pre-sale housing in Tiecheng
for the workers.

00:24:12.920 --> 00:24:14.110
The appraised value alone

00:24:14.110 --> 00:24:15.590
was higher than the buyout amount.

00:24:15.590 --> 00:24:17.850
Besides, that was against regulations.

00:24:18.680 --> 00:24:20.240
He then suggested an alternative.

00:24:20.240 --> 00:24:22.830
That was to lease the factory,
collect 5 years' rent in advance,

00:24:22.830 --> 00:24:26.400
and use that money to buy properties
from him so as to settle the workers.

00:24:26.400 --> 00:24:27.600
Anyway, I was puzzled

00:24:27.920 --> 00:24:29.380
by what he said at the time.

00:24:31.310 --> 00:24:32.240
Mr. Song, I...

00:24:32.270 --> 00:24:32.920
Well,

00:24:33.830 --> 00:24:35.360
don't stress yourself out.

00:24:35.920 --> 00:24:37.160
I'm fully aware

00:24:38.110 --> 00:24:41.110
that reviving this factory is no easy job.

00:24:42.310 --> 00:24:45.000
Seeing an old horse fall,
most people would come

00:24:45.110 --> 00:24:46.640
to carve out a piece of meat.

00:24:49.030 --> 00:24:50.360
I'm telling you all this

00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:52.450
just to get one message across:

00:24:52.510 --> 00:24:53.510
only those who truly have

00:24:53.510 --> 00:24:55.000
a soft spot for the East Chemical Factory

00:24:55.000 --> 00:24:56.920
would understand what I'm saying

00:24:57.240 --> 00:24:59.350
and keep this metaphorical old horse
that has contributed its all

00:24:59.350 --> 00:25:01.280
from being carved up and devoured.

00:25:05.310 --> 00:25:06.030
Mr. Zhuang!

00:25:11.880 --> 00:25:13.720
Mr. Zhuang, what are you doing here?

00:25:13.720 --> 00:25:14.960
Yan told me to come.

00:25:14.960 --> 00:25:16.490
He asked me to come help you.

00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:17.440
Help me?

00:25:17.590 --> 00:25:18.270
With what?

00:25:18.290 --> 00:25:19.980
Well, come with me.

00:25:20.400 --> 00:25:20.790
Okay.

00:25:21.110 --> 00:25:21.680
Let's go.

00:25:27.070 --> 00:25:28.960
Mr. Zhuang, what is happening?

00:25:29.400 --> 00:25:30.310
Yan!

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:32.110
Look who's here!

00:25:35.830 --> 00:25:37.430
Why did you come here so soon?

00:25:39.200 --> 00:25:39.880
Listen,

00:25:40.400 --> 00:25:42.240
give me three more days,

00:25:42.260 --> 00:25:45.180
and I guarantee these machines
will be as good as new

00:25:45.310 --> 00:25:46.840
when I hand them over to you.

00:25:47.310 --> 00:25:48.200
To me?

00:25:48.680 --> 00:25:49.400
Yes.

00:25:49.680 --> 00:25:52.280
We heard that you came back
to save the factory.

00:25:52.320 --> 00:25:54.480
While these old bones can still move,

00:25:54.680 --> 00:25:56.480
we'll do as much as we can to help you.

00:25:56.480 --> 00:25:57.940
-Exactly.
-That's right.

00:25:59.960 --> 00:26:01.160
You don't believe us?

00:26:01.510 --> 00:26:02.510
Listen up, fella.

00:26:02.920 --> 00:26:04.790
Though we're all getting older,

00:26:04.880 --> 00:26:06.940
we're still competent technicians.

00:26:07.850 --> 00:26:08.920
-This is a piece of cake for us.
-Right?

00:26:08.920 --> 00:26:09.400
Yes!

00:26:11.400 --> 00:26:12.510
Alright, let's get to work.

00:26:12.510 --> 00:26:13.160
Okay!

00:26:14.270 --> 00:26:15.160
Rest assured.

00:26:16.640 --> 00:26:18.240
If we can do a little bit more for you,

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:19.510
we will.

00:26:26.960 --> 00:26:27.750
Mr. Song,

00:26:28.030 --> 00:26:29.960
how long till the bidding ends?

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:31.550
Three months.

00:26:32.430 --> 00:26:33.360
Three months...

00:26:34.590 --> 00:26:36.310
Okay. Just give me some time.

00:26:36.480 --> 00:26:36.960
Okay.

00:26:49.030 --> 00:26:52.110
Mr. Kong, you assigned the acquisition
of Factory No. 3 to me with an excuse

00:26:52.110 --> 00:26:54.310
to revitalize underperforming assets.

00:26:54.310 --> 00:26:56.550
But in fact,
you were just looking for a scapegoat.

00:26:56.550 --> 00:26:58.980
You colluded with Fan Weijie
to raise the offer without consent,

00:26:58.980 --> 00:27:01.310
causing the company unnecessary losses.

00:27:01.640 --> 00:27:03.030
You're trying to shift all the blame to me

00:27:03.030 --> 00:27:06.000
as the headquarters is now pinpointing
who's responsible.

00:27:06.000 --> 00:27:08.240
I'll report all that happened truthfully.

00:27:08.240 --> 00:27:09.570
You'll have to deal with

00:27:09.830 --> 00:27:11.560
the losses caused by yourself.

00:27:12.310 --> 00:27:14.770
Taking blame, in essence,
is good training.

00:27:15.000 --> 00:27:17.550
Not everyone is qualified
to shoulder such a burden.

00:27:17.550 --> 00:27:19.510
I let you do it because I trust you.

00:27:19.750 --> 00:27:21.150
If you can make it through,

00:27:21.150 --> 00:27:23.510
you'll be only one step away
from the inner circle.

00:27:23.510 --> 00:27:25.550
Why destroy your future

00:27:25.550 --> 00:27:27.030
for some rundown factory?

00:27:27.310 --> 00:27:28.480
Investors must learn

00:27:28.480 --> 00:27:30.750
how to get the most out of every project.

00:27:30.830 --> 00:27:33.920
Clinging to something worthless
is real stupidity.

00:27:37.590 --> 00:27:38.850
You only see the price,

00:27:39.270 --> 00:27:40.510
yet I see the value.

00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:43.440
Factory No. 3 is not a bargaining chip
of yours.

00:27:43.440 --> 00:27:45.700
And I'm not a pawn
who you can push around.

00:27:50.400 --> 00:27:52.130
This is my resignation letter.

00:27:56.350 --> 00:28:02.030
Seems like... you're determined
to be a lone wolf,

00:28:02.270 --> 00:28:03.440
leaving yourself no way out.

00:28:03.440 --> 00:28:05.400
Your road ahead is quite rough.

00:28:08.140 --> 00:28:10.340
I've set my mind to revive Factory No. 3.

00:28:21.980 --> 00:28:22.780
Is it clicked?

00:28:23.000 --> 00:28:24.510
-Yes. Perfect.
-Sit down.

00:28:24.510 --> 00:28:25.440
Take your seats.

00:28:25.590 --> 00:28:27.720
Can't reach it from your seats, right?

00:28:29.350 --> 00:28:32.070
Honestly, I truly envy the three of you.

00:28:32.720 --> 00:28:34.750
See, you guys grew up together,

00:28:35.070 --> 00:28:37.090
went to school together,
and remain close till now.

00:28:37.090 --> 00:28:38.000
How very nice.

00:28:39.000 --> 00:28:39.550
Come on.

00:28:40.400 --> 00:28:42.660
This is to your everlasting friendship.

00:28:42.890 --> 00:28:44.480
To our everlasting friendship.

00:28:44.480 --> 00:28:45.930
To our everlasting friendship.

00:28:45.930 --> 00:28:47.530
To everlasting friendship.

00:28:56.510 --> 00:28:57.830
There is something...

00:28:58.070 --> 00:28:59.070
I need to tell you.

00:29:00.030 --> 00:29:01.430
You want to borrow money?

00:29:01.590 --> 00:29:02.650
That can't be true.

00:29:03.720 --> 00:29:06.070
Do I look like I'm in a position
to need a loan?

00:29:06.070 --> 00:29:08.330
You're the one who needs a loan, Xiaoman.

00:29:08.460 --> 00:29:09.390
I resigned.

00:29:11.790 --> 00:29:12.550
Why?

00:29:13.550 --> 00:29:15.670
Was the corporate mad about us asking you

00:29:15.670 --> 00:29:17.070
to acquire Factory No. 3?

00:29:17.330 --> 00:29:18.930
It had nothing to do with you.

00:29:19.640 --> 00:29:20.310
I resigned

00:29:20.310 --> 00:29:23.880
out of consideration for my future

00:29:24.200 --> 00:29:25.200
and my career.

00:29:26.310 --> 00:29:27.030
You know,

00:29:27.790 --> 00:29:29.050
it takes a little nudge

00:29:29.250 --> 00:29:31.380
for one to step out of his comfort zone.

00:29:31.790 --> 00:29:34.190
And you were the guys
who gave me that nudge.

00:29:34.560 --> 00:29:36.160
Here, a toast to you all.

00:29:36.310 --> 00:29:37.720
T-That was not our aim at all.

00:29:37.720 --> 00:29:39.520
It's difficult to find a job now.

00:29:39.750 --> 00:29:41.350
Have you thought it through?

00:29:42.110 --> 00:29:43.920
You'll have our support anyways.

00:29:43.920 --> 00:29:44.880
We're here for you.

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:46.510
Just let us know if you need anything.

00:29:46.510 --> 00:29:49.160
We'll do whatever we can to help.

00:29:49.160 --> 00:29:49.830
Okay.

00:29:50.550 --> 00:29:51.510
The current situation

00:29:51.510 --> 00:29:53.070
is truly worrying indeed.

00:29:53.830 --> 00:29:54.550
Just quickly

00:29:54.550 --> 00:29:57.210
think of a way
to ramp up the factory operations.

00:29:57.210 --> 00:29:59.530
If you need help, let us know anytime.

00:30:00.450 --> 00:30:01.910
Yes, that's also what I've been thinking.

00:30:01.910 --> 00:30:03.880
I plan to meet with Mr. Song tomorrow.

00:30:03.880 --> 00:30:04.350
Okay.

00:30:04.960 --> 00:30:05.590
Oh, right.

00:30:06.590 --> 00:30:07.990
I'd like to show you something.

00:30:07.990 --> 00:30:08.530
What is it?

00:30:08.530 --> 00:30:10.960
I interviewed
some old workers of the factory.

00:30:10.960 --> 00:30:12.340
Listen to what they said.

00:30:12.340 --> 00:30:13.540
What is it? Let me see.

00:30:13.670 --> 00:30:14.670
I'll check it out.

00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:21.350
As long as we're united,

00:30:23.950 --> 00:30:26.300
the factory will never fall apart.

00:30:27.790 --> 00:30:28.920
Neither will

00:30:29.590 --> 00:30:30.720
this collective.

00:30:34.680 --> 00:30:35.270
Xia Lei.

00:30:38.030 --> 00:30:39.510
Look at these old workers.

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:41.550
Each of them is like a screw.

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:43.660
Only when they're installed
in the correct positions

00:30:43.660 --> 00:30:45.790
by someone who truly understands them

00:30:45.920 --> 00:30:48.270
can their value be maximized.

00:30:49.000 --> 00:30:51.640
I think you are the person
who truly understands them.

00:30:51.640 --> 00:30:53.240
You see, you've been working

00:30:53.460 --> 00:30:55.720
on the front lines
of industrial investment.

00:30:55.720 --> 00:30:57.310
I bet you know the value

00:30:57.960 --> 00:31:00.240
of these old workers and Factory No. 3

00:31:00.240 --> 00:31:01.880
better than Xiaoman and I do.

00:31:02.410 --> 00:31:04.070
You'll definitely nail this.

00:31:04.590 --> 00:31:05.720
We believe you will.

00:31:07.700 --> 00:31:08.540
Yes, we do.

00:31:10.680 --> 00:31:12.940
Gosh, this video is really getting me...

00:31:13.590 --> 00:31:14.630
feel nostalgic.

00:31:14.980 --> 00:31:16.910
It has even reminded me of the past.

00:31:17.840 --> 00:31:18.840
-Stop watching it then.
-Come on, guys.

00:31:18.840 --> 00:31:20.240
Yeah. Raise our glasses.

00:31:20.270 --> 00:31:21.510
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

00:31:21.830 --> 00:31:22.350
Cheers.

00:31:25.950 --> 00:31:26.480
I'm not leaving.

00:31:26.480 --> 00:31:27.720
-Look at them.
-It's Zhuang and the guys.

00:31:27.720 --> 00:31:28.790
Making a fuss here every day.

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:30.110
-Yeah.
-I'm not leaving anyway.

00:31:30.110 --> 00:31:30.790
Seriously.

00:31:30.790 --> 00:31:32.430
I heard you yelling from miles away.

00:31:32.430 --> 00:31:33.790
You're the loudest of all.

00:31:33.790 --> 00:31:35.510
Chief Engineer Yan,
back from grocery shopping?

00:31:35.510 --> 00:31:36.770
Uncle Yan, Auntie Han.

00:31:39.620 --> 00:31:40.820
Who is this young man?

00:31:42.790 --> 00:31:44.000
Nobody but my boy.

00:31:44.640 --> 00:31:46.400
He's Zhuang's son.

00:31:48.040 --> 00:31:49.170
You're all grown up.

00:31:49.510 --> 00:31:51.510
I haven't seen you for years.

00:31:51.750 --> 00:31:52.950
What brings you back?

00:31:53.150 --> 00:31:55.830
I came back to take my dad to Hainan.

00:31:55.920 --> 00:31:56.880
For a fun trip?

00:31:57.850 --> 00:31:58.410
No.

00:31:58.720 --> 00:31:59.720
Not for a fun trip.

00:31:59.720 --> 00:32:00.920
Isn't the factory about to be relocated?

00:32:00.920 --> 00:32:01.680
Nonsense, you brat.

00:32:01.680 --> 00:32:02.440
What did he just say?

00:32:02.440 --> 00:32:03.500
-Nothing.
-What was that gibberish?

00:32:03.500 --> 00:32:04.160
Gibberish.

00:32:04.480 --> 00:32:05.720
Now that I'm retired,

00:32:05.720 --> 00:32:07.520
my son wants me to move to Hainan.

00:32:08.480 --> 00:32:09.210
Sounds good.

00:32:09.310 --> 00:32:11.070
That's a lovely place to settle in.
The weather's good there.

00:32:11.070 --> 00:32:11.920
Yes, it's warm.

00:32:11.920 --> 00:32:13.680
Yan, shall we go home now?

00:32:13.680 --> 00:32:14.790
Okay. Let's go.

00:32:14.790 --> 00:32:15.440
See you later.

00:32:15.440 --> 00:32:17.310
Come visit us when you have time.

00:32:17.720 --> 00:32:18.920
Take good care of your dad.

00:32:18.920 --> 00:32:20.590
-Bye, Chief Engineer Yan.
-Take care.

00:32:20.590 --> 00:32:21.070
Sure.

00:32:23.980 --> 00:32:25.510
What were you babbling about?

00:32:25.510 --> 00:32:26.310
Just the relocation.

00:32:26.310 --> 00:32:27.970
-To Yingkou, right?
-Shut up!

00:32:31.270 --> 00:32:31.790
Dad.

00:32:33.790 --> 00:32:34.680
is Uncle Yan...

00:32:36.240 --> 00:32:37.200
sick?

00:32:40.280 --> 00:32:41.280
Let's play chess.

00:32:56.720 --> 00:32:57.510
Yan.

00:32:58.590 --> 00:33:00.190
Have some soy milk, will you?

00:33:01.640 --> 00:33:02.480
Yan,

00:33:02.970 --> 00:33:04.040
are you okay?

00:33:08.390 --> 00:33:10.440
Sweetie, what should we do?

00:33:10.440 --> 00:33:11.510
I'm so worried.

00:33:11.970 --> 00:33:13.610
Since he found out about the relocation,

00:33:13.610 --> 00:33:14.860
he has talked much less

00:33:14.860 --> 00:33:16.120
and stopped going out.

00:33:20.310 --> 00:33:23.270
According to a school mate of mine
who studied medicine,

00:33:23.270 --> 00:33:24.720
Dad is acting this way

00:33:24.920 --> 00:33:26.510
because he feels insecure.

00:33:27.010 --> 00:33:30.380
That makes sense.
He spent decades working in the factory.

00:33:30.790 --> 00:33:33.390
If it's gone,
it'll be like his home is gone too.

00:33:33.920 --> 00:33:35.780
But he can't stay at home forever.

00:33:36.160 --> 00:33:37.560
It is the doctor's advice

00:33:37.720 --> 00:33:40.120
that he should often go out
and walk around.

00:33:40.230 --> 00:33:41.690
Take him out for a walk now.

00:33:45.240 --> 00:33:46.030
Dad,

00:33:46.510 --> 00:33:47.840
won't you eat anything?

00:33:48.240 --> 00:33:50.170
Just grab a bite. The food's ready.

00:33:56.570 --> 00:33:58.300
How about we go out for a stroll?

00:34:01.680 --> 00:34:02.510
Just a walk outside.

00:34:02.510 --> 00:34:04.440
You can't stay at home all the time.

00:34:04.520 --> 00:34:06.720
Think of it as a favor for me.
I want to go.

00:34:06.920 --> 00:34:07.440
Okay?

00:34:07.440 --> 00:34:10.100
Your daughter...
Your daughter wants to go out.

00:34:10.110 --> 00:34:11.590
Keep me company, will you?

00:34:11.590 --> 00:34:12.400
Please.

00:34:13.280 --> 00:34:15.940
-Keep me company then. It's a deal.
-Yes, I will.

00:34:16.480 --> 00:34:17.480
I'll go get changed.

00:34:17.480 --> 00:34:18.480
Wait for a moment.

00:34:28.110 --> 00:34:28.630
Dad.

00:34:29.389 --> 00:34:31.620
Morning air is fresh, isn't it?

00:34:32.590 --> 00:34:34.389
It feels nice to be out for a walk.

00:34:36.000 --> 00:34:37.710
Where would you like to go?
I'll go with you.

00:34:37.710 --> 00:34:38.840
No, I'll go with you.

00:34:44.330 --> 00:34:46.080
Why is no one around?

00:34:47.510 --> 00:34:49.040
What is everyone busy with?

00:34:49.920 --> 00:34:50.949
Moving houses?

00:34:52.010 --> 00:34:53.000
That can't be it.

00:34:53.000 --> 00:34:55.590
It's so early.
They're either still sleeping

00:34:55.960 --> 00:34:58.190
or having breakfast at home.

00:35:03.920 --> 00:35:04.720
Let's go home.

00:35:07.230 --> 00:35:09.760
Dad!
Dad, we've only been out for a moment.

00:35:09.760 --> 00:35:10.670
Wait up!

00:35:12.600 --> 00:35:14.770
Xiaodan, if we let Uncle Yan go to work,

00:35:15.070 --> 00:35:16.590
will it be of any help?

00:35:17.880 --> 00:35:19.920
That way, at least Uncle will go out.

00:35:21.190 --> 00:35:22.590
Staying at home every day

00:35:22.670 --> 00:35:24.510
will only worsen his condition.

00:35:27.480 --> 00:35:28.480
Let him go to work?

00:35:28.590 --> 00:35:29.510
How?

00:35:29.590 --> 00:35:31.390
Nobody works in the factory now.

00:35:32.470 --> 00:35:35.020
Aren't there many old factory workers
around?

00:35:35.020 --> 00:35:36.800
We can have them gathered and put on

00:35:36.800 --> 00:35:38.110
a show for Chief Engineer Yan.

00:35:38.110 --> 00:35:39.480
It'll be wonderful.

00:35:40.070 --> 00:35:42.510
W-Will this plan work?

00:35:42.990 --> 00:35:44.120
It definitely will.

00:35:44.320 --> 00:35:46.400
I'll ask my dad to help.

00:35:46.710 --> 00:35:48.440
He'll assemble workers for us.

00:35:48.760 --> 00:35:49.490
Don't worry.

00:35:49.510 --> 00:35:50.510
I'll take control

00:35:50.710 --> 00:35:51.970
as the chief director.

00:35:52.590 --> 00:35:54.520
Even no lunch boxes will be needed.

00:35:56.510 --> 00:35:57.510
Nice and slow. Careful.

00:35:57.510 --> 00:35:59.000
Okay. Mind your hands.

00:36:01.870 --> 00:36:02.670
It's through.

00:36:05.070 --> 00:36:06.000
Watch the steps.

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:07.470
Xiaodan,

00:36:08.480 --> 00:36:09.480
look what I found.

00:36:09.920 --> 00:36:10.850
A drawing board!

00:36:11.480 --> 00:36:14.140
That's the most important thing
in this office.

00:36:19.430 --> 00:36:20.430
Such a big bundle.

00:36:21.920 --> 00:36:23.760
Let me place the drawings here.

00:36:26.190 --> 00:36:27.790
Everyone is in position now.

00:36:28.070 --> 00:36:30.000
I'd like to give some instructions

00:36:30.240 --> 00:36:31.170
as the director.

00:36:32.400 --> 00:36:34.230
Uncle Sun, you'll sweep the floor.

00:36:34.230 --> 00:36:34.510
Got it.

00:36:34.510 --> 00:36:35.190
Mr. Zhou,

00:36:35.400 --> 00:36:37.110
you'll clean up the garbage.

00:36:37.230 --> 00:36:37.710
Got it.

00:36:38.030 --> 00:36:39.090
You two gentlemen,

00:36:39.110 --> 00:36:41.440
when you see Chief Engineer Yan, say this:

00:36:41.630 --> 00:36:43.290
"Hello, Chief Engineer Yan."

00:36:43.440 --> 00:36:44.630
Then walk towards the outside.

00:36:44.630 --> 00:36:45.840
Yes, good posture.

00:36:45.840 --> 00:36:46.230
Okay.

00:36:46.230 --> 00:36:47.090
Keep it in mind.

00:36:47.280 --> 00:36:48.210
That's about it.

00:36:49.320 --> 00:36:50.120
Here he comes!

00:36:50.440 --> 00:36:51.590
-Chief Engineer Yan's coming this way.
-Dad!

00:36:51.590 --> 00:36:53.390
Chief Engineer Yan has arrived.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:57.110
Good morning, Chief Engineer Yan!

00:36:57.110 --> 00:36:58.110
Good morning.

00:36:58.960 --> 00:36:59.820
Morning shift?

00:36:59.960 --> 00:37:00.670
Yes.

00:37:02.760 --> 00:37:03.440
Alright.

00:37:05.830 --> 00:37:06.560
Sprinkle some water.

00:37:06.560 --> 00:37:08.150
Chief Engineer Yan,
you're here for work too?

00:37:08.150 --> 00:37:09.280
So much dust being kicked up.

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:10.030
Sprinkle some water.

00:37:10.030 --> 00:37:10.480
Got it.

00:37:10.480 --> 00:37:11.230
I'm on it!

00:37:22.510 --> 00:37:24.110
You all acted very well.

00:37:24.710 --> 00:37:26.630
Excellent. Impressive.

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:27.770
-Hey...
-Go ahead.

00:37:27.770 --> 00:37:29.320
It's really hard to be an actor.

00:37:29.320 --> 00:37:31.190
I didn't even know how to walk just now.

00:37:31.190 --> 00:37:32.520
You did great, Mr. Zhou.

00:37:36.710 --> 00:37:37.320
Come in.

00:37:42.110 --> 00:37:43.640
Hello, Chief Engineer Yan.

00:37:43.920 --> 00:37:45.360
I am the new engineer.

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:51.510
New engineer?

00:37:53.360 --> 00:37:55.280
HR didn't inform me. How come?

00:37:56.320 --> 00:37:58.580
Maybe the notice hasn't reached you yet.

00:37:59.070 --> 00:38:00.530
I'm here in person anyway.

00:38:01.270 --> 00:38:02.270
Welcome onboard.

00:38:03.190 --> 00:38:04.520
W-What's your surname?

00:38:04.670 --> 00:38:07.000
It's "Zhuang." My full name is Zhuang Lin.

00:38:08.590 --> 00:38:09.480
"Zhuang Lin"?

00:38:10.590 --> 00:38:12.440
There's a senior worker here—

00:38:13.070 --> 00:38:15.400
our best turner—named Zhuang Dalin.

00:38:15.670 --> 00:38:16.900
His name's quite similar to yours.

00:38:16.900 --> 00:38:17.920
What a coincidence.

00:38:17.920 --> 00:38:18.670
R-Really?

00:38:19.440 --> 00:38:22.710
I guess I'm destined to work
in the East Chemical Plant then.

00:38:22.710 --> 00:38:24.320
Which school did you go to?

00:38:24.440 --> 00:38:26.110
The second branch of Beijing Film Academy.

00:38:26.110 --> 00:38:26.670
What?

00:38:27.510 --> 00:38:27.920
Beijing...

00:38:27.920 --> 00:38:29.440
Electrical Engineering Academy.

00:38:29.440 --> 00:38:31.410
The second branch
of Beijing Electrical Engineering Academy.

00:38:31.410 --> 00:38:33.360
Beijing Electrical Engineering Academy?

00:38:33.360 --> 00:38:35.710
Since when has there been such an academy
in Beijing?

00:38:35.710 --> 00:38:36.510
It's new.

00:38:41.070 --> 00:38:41.920
Zhuang!

00:38:43.230 --> 00:38:44.030
Come in here.

00:38:45.880 --> 00:38:47.610
Chief Engineer Yan, what's up?

00:38:48.840 --> 00:38:52.040
I can see you've been hanging around
in the office all day.

00:38:52.320 --> 00:38:54.720
Why don't you inspect the workshops
at all?

00:38:54.840 --> 00:38:56.040
I've done it already.

00:38:56.690 --> 00:38:59.400
Everyone is in high spirits.

00:38:59.420 --> 00:39:01.030
I'm not asking about the people,

00:39:01.030 --> 00:39:02.110
but the equipment.

00:39:02.400 --> 00:39:05.060
Is the reactor temperature
within safe limits?

00:39:05.110 --> 00:39:06.840
Any risks of leakage?

00:39:07.320 --> 00:39:09.030
The data of safety valves

00:39:09.110 --> 00:39:11.770
and pressure gauges must be recorded
every day.

00:39:13.230 --> 00:39:14.430
Bring me the logbook.

00:39:15.030 --> 00:39:16.050
I'll go get it done now.

00:39:16.050 --> 00:39:16.860
I'm on it.

00:39:17.510 --> 00:39:19.310
I'll leave you to your work then.

00:39:37.110 --> 00:39:37.170
I had no idea
there would be so much involved

00:39:37.170 --> 00:39:39.480
[Eight's Electric Vehicle Retail]

00:39:39.480 --> 00:39:41.060
in making an electric vehicle.

00:39:41.060 --> 00:39:43.510
Two hours of charging
gives this thing 80 km of range.

00:39:43.510 --> 00:39:45.320
A vehicle like this lasts
at least 5 years.

00:39:45.320 --> 00:39:46.710
And the best part—it's eco-friendly.

00:39:46.710 --> 00:39:47.320
After it's scrapped,

00:39:47.320 --> 00:39:49.380
90% of the materials can be recycled.

00:39:50.320 --> 00:39:51.070
Hold on.

00:39:51.420 --> 00:39:54.040
Battery performance hinges on
the electrolyte's ability to conduct

00:39:54.040 --> 00:39:54.920
lithium ions, right?

00:39:54.920 --> 00:39:57.000
Now, are we still relying on imports

00:39:57.230 --> 00:39:58.690
for advanced electrolyte formulas?

00:39:58.690 --> 00:40:01.510
Yes. The old ones provided
poor thermal stability,

00:40:01.510 --> 00:40:03.040
and the new ones are costly.

00:40:04.190 --> 00:40:04.880
Dad!

00:40:07.110 --> 00:40:07.800
What's up?

00:40:08.480 --> 00:40:09.800
Do you know about lithium batteries?

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:10.530
Yes.

00:40:11.150 --> 00:40:12.550
I'm not behind the times.

00:40:13.630 --> 00:40:14.480
Why do you ask?

00:40:16.290 --> 00:40:17.520
I have a target now.

00:40:19.320 --> 00:40:21.450
My focus will be on lithium batteries.

00:40:23.050 --> 00:40:25.650
Our factory used to process chemicals,
right?

00:40:25.920 --> 00:40:28.540
The production lines and equipment
probably still work.

00:40:28.540 --> 00:40:30.400
I think I have a feasible plan now.

00:40:32.070 --> 00:40:33.270
Get ready for dinner.

00:40:33.800 --> 00:40:34.440
Okay!

00:40:54.610 --> 00:40:55.420
Hello, Mr. Li.

00:40:57.230 --> 00:40:59.710
Have you read my proposal?

00:41:02.590 --> 00:41:03.510
Oh, you have.

00:41:04.440 --> 00:41:05.710
You're very interested?

00:41:05.710 --> 00:41:06.910
T-That's great news.

00:41:07.030 --> 00:41:07.800
Yes, yes.

00:41:08.000 --> 00:41:08.480
Right.

00:41:09.320 --> 00:41:09.720
Right.

00:41:10.280 --> 00:41:11.480
It's about new energy.

00:41:11.480 --> 00:41:13.280
Lithium battery electrolytes.

00:41:13.550 --> 00:41:15.920
The country is promoting new energy now.

00:41:16.070 --> 00:41:18.400
Electrolytes are key to lithium batteries.

00:41:18.400 --> 00:41:19.800
The market demand for them is huge,

00:41:19.800 --> 00:41:21.760
and the profits are highly promising.

00:41:21.760 --> 00:41:24.630
Our factory used to process
and produce chemicals.

00:41:24.710 --> 00:41:26.390
The old equipment will be good to go
after a retrofit.

00:41:26.390 --> 00:41:28.810
We also have a ready-made
environmental protection system,

00:41:28.810 --> 00:41:31.230
which will save much cost
in the initial stages.

00:41:31.230 --> 00:41:32.470
The profit potential

00:41:32.470 --> 00:41:33.800
is huge and strong.

00:41:34.960 --> 00:41:35.670
Yes, yes.

00:41:37.340 --> 00:41:39.220
Well then, I'll cut to the chase.

00:41:39.760 --> 00:41:43.630
I-I'm currently
in need of financial support.

00:41:46.400 --> 00:41:47.030
Really?

00:41:48.030 --> 00:41:49.320
Great. Well...

00:41:49.370 --> 00:41:51.640
I'll send you the capital usage plan,

00:41:51.670 --> 00:41:53.300
the equity allocation proposal,

00:41:53.300 --> 00:41:54.820
and the business plan.

00:41:55.110 --> 00:41:55.760
Okay?

00:41:58.630 --> 00:42:00.630
-Yan, you’re back.
-I’m off work.

00:42:00.840 --> 00:42:02.570
We're having dumplings today?

00:42:02.590 --> 00:42:03.190
Yeah.

00:42:03.190 --> 00:42:03.670
Good.

00:42:04.030 --> 00:42:05.560
You worked overtime again?

00:42:05.590 --> 00:42:06.840
Yes, had to work late again.

00:42:06.840 --> 00:42:07.670
God knows what's going on.

00:42:07.670 --> 00:42:09.110
There has been so work in the factory
lately.

00:42:09.110 --> 00:42:10.070
I'm needed for everything.

00:42:10.070 --> 00:42:10.880
People turn to me

00:42:10.880 --> 00:42:12.670
even for things outside my scope of work.

00:42:12.670 --> 00:42:13.840
That proves you're the authority.

00:42:13.840 --> 00:42:14.760
Everyone needs your advice.

00:42:14.760 --> 00:42:15.960
-Anyway, I…
-You're doing a great job.

00:42:15.960 --> 00:42:17.030
I've figured out one thing—

00:42:17.030 --> 00:42:18.880
the factory can't run without me.

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:20.510
-Yes.
-You're just indispensable.

00:42:20.510 --> 00:42:21.400
Go wash up, Dad.

00:42:21.400 --> 00:42:22.480
-Okay.
-We'll have dumplings later.

00:42:22.480 --> 00:42:23.150
Got it.

00:42:24.110 --> 00:42:24.710
Sweetie.

00:42:26.070 --> 00:42:28.280
You need to talk to Zhuang Sen.

00:42:28.480 --> 00:42:31.190
Tell him not to tire your dad out
with extra scenes.

00:42:31.190 --> 00:42:32.790
I've made it very clear to him

00:42:32.920 --> 00:42:35.130
that my dad must clock out
when working hours are over.

00:42:35.130 --> 00:42:36.840
Yeah.
Then why does your dad still work late?

00:42:36.840 --> 00:42:37.640
You know what?

00:42:38.320 --> 00:42:40.250
The workers gathered by Zhuang Sen

00:42:40.510 --> 00:42:41.700
are even more enthusiastic

00:42:41.700 --> 00:42:43.400
than Dad in these scenes.

00:42:43.710 --> 00:42:44.800
They're zealous.

00:42:45.320 --> 00:42:46.520
I'm just thinking...

00:42:46.630 --> 00:42:48.690
the factory did use to be boisterous.

00:42:48.880 --> 00:42:49.800
So much...

00:42:49.840 --> 00:42:50.840
-So much was going on.
-But now it isn't operating.

00:42:50.840 --> 00:42:51.510
Yeah.

00:42:51.670 --> 00:42:54.000
Everyone's bored and wants to work again.

00:42:54.590 --> 00:42:58.320
So they play along with our plan
and even make Dad stay for overtime.

00:42:59.360 --> 00:43:01.400
Don't forget to make some chili oil.

00:43:01.400 --> 00:43:03.110
Okay, got it.